com.variant.client.servlet.impl

Class ServletSessionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.variant.client.servlet.impl.ServletSessionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ServletSession

    public class ServletSessionImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ServletSession

    The implementation of ServletSession. Replaces bare client's VariantCoreSession#targetForState(com.variant.core.xdm.State) method with one, which returns the servlet-aware implementation of VariantCoreStateRequest.
